sequenceDiagram
    participant FS as File System
    participant Scan as Scanner (Goroutine)
    participant Analyze as Analysis Stage
    participant Queue as Repair Queue
    participant SLM as Repair Workers (llama.cpp)
    participant Valid as Validation Stage

    FS->>Scan: Read Go File
    Scan->>Analyze: Parsed Tree-sitter AST
    Analyze->>Analyze: Run SCM Queries
    Analyze->>Analyze: AST Slicing (<1024 tokens)
    Analyze->>Queue: Send Syntax Independent Unit (SIU)
    Queue->>SLM: Pull SIU for processing
    SLM->>SLM: Prompt Qwen2.5-Coder-1.5B
    SLM->>Valid: Proposed Code Patch
    Valid->>Valid: In-memory Tree.Edit
    alt is Valid?
        Valid->>FS: Apply syntactically correct patch
    else Error Detected
        Valid->>SLM: Extract S-Expression & Reprompt (up to 3x)
    end
